<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV86">
<l>māṇikkaṅ koṇṭu kuraṅkeṟi vottiru ḷōṭumuṭṭi</l>
<l>yāṇippoṉ ṉaṉṉa cuṭarpaṭu mālai yulakaḷanta</l>
<l>māṇikka mēyeṉ marakata mēmaṟṟop pāraiyillā</l>
<l>vāṇippoṉ ṉēyaṭi yēṉuṭai yāvi yaṭaikkalamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who once rid Hara of the food from a flesh[-reeking] vessel, called the head</l>
<l>of the Unborn one from the high lotus blossom as a refuge, you who raises as weapons</l>
<l>discus [and] conch, you who were held in place by the cowherdess’s strong tethers</l>
<l>that day, because of the butter, speaking what shall I lament our lord?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
